snippet.title: ACE COMBAT 7: Skies Unknown – 3rd Anniversary Trailer
snippet.description:
To celebrate its 3rd Anniversary, a free update is available now to all #ACE7 players! This update features a payload of new cosmetics, including fourteen new skins, a new callsign, and seventeen new emblems!

Play ACE COMBAT 7: Skies Unknown today! http://spr.ly/6059zN0Wf 

#ACECOMBAT
